PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (SAHOYUÉ - ?EHADCHO (GRIZZLY BEAR MOUNTAIN AND SCENTED GRASS HILLS), NATIONAL HISTORIC SITE, N.W.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of some 5,550 square kilometres of land in the Northwest Territories; and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made in 2001.
